{"tid":595463,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求救: 歐洲老佬email俾offer我，接受左之後又唔見佢回，咁即係請定唔請？","createTime":"2018-03-16T16:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T18:59:39.000Z","uid":176919,"like":1,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"8d77b59c1881c6486448dd57635beac68cad70aa","tid":595463,"uid":176919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"情況係前日見完，下午收到email俾offer，但我第2日見第2份工前先睇到email，都已經lunch time覆，不過沉日見佢冇覆我reconfirm，我以為佢withdraw offer，我冇打電話去問or再send email去追。   咁今日就繼續見工。<br />\n點個夜晚同朋友講開，佢就話個老闆已經當請實左我，因為歐洲人做法一向係咁，叫我星期一按之前傾好的日子照返工。<br />\n問題就黎喇，如果我星期一真係上去，萬一佢唔係請我咪尷尬死？<br />\n但係如果我唔去，掉轉頭佢真係請我，我咪又俾左個壞印象佢？<br />\n求救各位巴絲打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nemail節錄如下:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">意大利老闆:<br />\nThank you for coming to the interview today and I hereby offer you the potential employment with our company with basic terms as follows:<br />\nPost: Secretary<br />\nDay of commencement: At your earliest convenience (e.g. Monday, 19 March 2018 could be an option for us)<br />\nBasic salary: HK$XXXXX / month <br />\nWorking hours: 9am~5pm &ndash; (Monday to Friday)<br />\nAnnual leave: 10 working days<br />\n1 month notice of termination of employment is required after probation by employee and employer<br />\nMedical benefits: as provided to Company&rsquo;s staff<br />\n <br />\nIf you agree with the above terms, we will prepare the formal employment agreement for your review.<br />\n<br />\nI look forward to hearing from you soon. Should you have any questions in relation to the above, please do not hesitate to contact me.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我的回覆:<br />\nIt was pleasant to be interviewed by you yesterday and I&rsquo;m writing to formally accept your job offer for the position of Secretary at XXX Limited. <br />\n<br />\nAs discussed, my starting salary will be HK$XXXXX per month and 10 workings days annual leave. I would join your organization on 19 March 2018. It is appreciated that if you can send me formal employment contract for the other details.<br />\n<br />\nIf there&rsquo;s anything you need from me prior to that start date, or any documents I should bring on my first day, please let me know.</span></span>"},{"pid":"489c2f13f2fbaa39577028fcc32e002225e82667","tid":595463,"uid":29218,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"你咪上去望下囉<br />\n驚咩?"},{"pid":"c11d7dbacb343885ee7e307704b79d424138a3ac","tid":595463,"uid":59283,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"叫佢整份draft contract比你簽左先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec6c9960c03a1f106419c87ec3941c7acd72dc9","tid":595463,"uid":115264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"問佢份contract開工前簽定個日朝早簽"},{"pid":"2a4b45d5ede9b241a932f64948bc16554b58470f","tid":595463,"uid":38572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"上去喇 驚條春?"},{"pid":"124195aacb8ec0f690ad12cf3fe1ef29ee3faae2","tid":595463,"uid":176919,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"quote":{"pid":"489c2f13f2fbaa39577028fcc32e002225e82667","tid":595463,"uid":29218,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"你咪上去望下囉<br />\n驚咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"驚瘀，如果佢同時請左第2個仲灶火羅"},{"pid":"101a64ac833c7dc030ef446d91a6be460ddd4f52","tid":595463,"uid":99642,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:16:30.000Z","msg":"緊張咪打電話問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁大個人少少野都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/fa